<p>24 June, 2002<br>
5 PM</p>

<p><a href="http://www.linux.org.pe/conferencia/">Auditorio de la Asamblea Nacional de Rectores</a></p>

<p>Hosted by <a href="http://www.linux.org.pe/">Grupo de Usuarios de Linux de Perú</a>, the Partnership of Users and Developer of Free Software (sponsored by <a href="http://www.unesco.org.uy/informatica/consorcio/index.html">UNESCO</a>), and the Faculty of Engineering of the <a href="http://www.ucu.edu.uy">Catholic University</a></p>

